  description: 'A heavy blade infused with eternal frost. It chills enemies to the
    bone.

    <b><color=#8E44AD>[E]</color></b> Frost Strike: Launches a forward
    ice wave that damages enemies and freezes them in place.

    <b><color=#8E44AD>[Q]</color></b>
    Glacial Sigil: Opens a frost circle above you and rains homing ice balls onto
    nearby enemies.'
